    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just a moment of rest though. like, every time i try to \"step back,\" the pressure just catches up to me again. there's no actual peace. it feels like the only way to actually get away from all this noise and constant failure is to just... not be here anymore. does that even make sense? i just feel like i've run out of options.",
