      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but it feels like you're just talking about survival, not actually finding peace. survival is just more of the same grinding exhaustion. when i say i want it to stop, i mean the constant weight of existing when everything you worked for is gone. it's like i'm just waiting for a relief that's never coming. it's hard to believe in \"pain ending\" when the pain is just my life now.",
